OL,5,G1100 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's a feisty old payment day
OL,7,     Fafter a week packed to the gills
OL,8,     Fwith gripes. You could cut the
OL,9,     Ftension with a knife! Fortunately,
OL,10,     Fwe haven't given any of them
OL,11,     Fknives.
